<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>仙缘布告</title>
<style>
/* 引入外部书法字体 */
@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=ZCOOL+KuaiLe&display=swap');

/* --- 关键修改区域 --- */

body, html {
margin: 0;
padding: 0;
width: 100%;
/* 使用 min-height 确保在任何情况下容器都至少有屏幕那么高，兼容性更好 */
min-height: 100vh;
font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", "Microsoft YaHei", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif;
background-color: #1a1a1a;
background-image: url('https://youke1.picui.cn/s1/2025/07/19/687accde53dc6.png');
background-size: cover;
background-position: center;
background-attachment: fixed;
/* Flex 布局用于完美居中 */
display: flex;
justify-content: center;
align-items: center;
/* 给外层留一点边距，防止卷轴紧贴屏幕边缘 */
padding: 20px;
box-sizing: border-box;
}

.bulletin-container {
width: 100%;
/* 增加了最大宽度，让卷轴在宽屏上显得更大 */
max-width: 1000px;
position: relative;
/* 移除固定高度，让其由内容自适应撑开 */
/* 为上下卷轴留出空间 */
padding: 30px 0;
filter: drop-shadow(0 0 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.5));
}

.scroll-content {
background-color: #f5eecf; /* 仿宣纸颜色 */
background-image: url('https://www.transparenttextures.com/patterns/paper-fibers.png'); /* 纸张纹理 */
border: 2px solid #c9a87c;
padding: 40px 50px; /* 调整内部文字边距 */
color: #4a3a2a;
box-shadow: inset 0 0 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
/* 核心！设置最大高度，内容超过这个高度后，会出现内部滚动条 */
max-height: 80vh;
overflow-y: auto; /* 当内容溢出时，显示垂直滚动条 */
}

/* --- 修改结束 --- */


/* 模拟卷轴的上下两端 */
.scroll-roller {
position: absolute;
left: -15px;
right: -15px;
height: 30px;
background-color: #5a3e2b; /* 暗木色 */
background-image: linear-gradient(45deg, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 25%, transparent 25%, transparent 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 50%, rgba(255,255,255,0.1) 75%, transparent 75%, transparent);
border: 2px solid #3d2a1d;
border-radius: 5px;
box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.4);
}

.scroll-roller.top {
top: 10px;
}

.scroll-roller.bottom {
bottom: 10px;
}

.title {
font-family: 'ZCOOL KuaiLe', cursive;
font-size: 2.5em;
text-align: center;
color: #8c3a3a;
margin-top: 0;
margin-bottom: 20px;
letter-spacing: 5px;
}

.content-list {
list-style: none;
padding-left: 0;
counter-reset: item-counter;
}

.content-list li {
margin-bottom: 15px;
line-height: 1.8;
padding-left: 45px;
position: relative;
}

.content-list li::before {
counter-increment: item-counter;
content: "其" counter(item-counter, cjk-ideographic) "、";
position: absolute;
left: 0;
top: 0;
font-weight: bold;
color: #8c6a48;
}

.highlight {
color: #c0392b;
font-weight: bold;
}

.signature-area {
margin-top: 30px;
text-align: right;
font-size: 1em;
position: relative;
}

.author-name {
display: block;
margin-bottom: 5px;
}

.seal {
display: inline-block;
width: 40px;
height: 40px;
background-color: #c0392b;
color: #f5eecf;
font-family: 'ZCOOL KuaiLe', cursive;
font-size: 28px;
line-height: 40px;
text-align: center;
border: 3px solid #a52a2a;
border-radius: 3px;
transform: rotate(-10deg);
box-shadow: 1px 1px 3px rgba(0,0,0,0.3);
margin-right: 10px;
user-select: none;
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="bulletin-container">
<div class="scroll-roller top"></div>
<div class="scroll-content">
<h1 class="title">告知道友书</h1>

<ul class="content-list">
<li>作者<span class="highlight">【LUCKLYJKOP】</span>，此卡当前为 <span class="highlight">1.6 正式版本</span>。欢迎各位道友前来体验，若有意进行二次创作，烦请先行联系。</li>
<li><span class="highlight">重要：</span>创建存档之后，首要之事并非开始游玩，而是前往<span class="highlight">【设置】</span>，将您预设的<span class="highlight">【正则】</span>导入，此步至关重要！注意，是创建存档后，在前端的设置里导入正则，不要导入预设的总结/摘要部分正则</li>
<li>【总结】功能可自定义提示词。若使用父窗口总结，请务必开启预设中自带的总结功能，以得最佳体验。云酒馆开始不了游戏可以试试夸克浏览器</li>
<li>此卡目前依<span class="highlight">《凡人修仙传》</span>世界观构筑了人界篇内容。</li>
<li>此卡内建变量储存与更新机制。为免冲突，请<span class="highlight">关闭【表格插件】及【预设的表格适配】</span>。另，总结请务必使用前端自带之功能。</li>
<li><span class="highlight">向右滑动，即可开启您的修仙之旅。</span>欢迎提出宝贵建议，此卡耗时四日而成，前端制作不易，望道友们多多点赞支持！</li>
</ul>

<div class="signature-area">
<span class="author-name">lucklyjkop</span>
<div class="seal">著</div>
</div>

</div>
<div class="scroll-roller bottom"></div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
```

